<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href={{ url_for('static', filename='css/html5reset.css') }}>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href={{ url_for('static', filename='css/game_res.css') }}>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href={{ url_for('static', filename='image/video-camera.png') }} >

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alegreya+Sans+SC&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Permanent+Marker&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Kevin Bacon Game</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <p class="title" id="logo">It's Movier</p>
        <nav>
            <ul class="nav_links">
                <li><a href="http://127.0.0.1:5000/game" id="current"  class="nav_item">Kevin Bacon Game</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://127.0.0.1:5000/popular" class="nav_item">Score</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://127.0.0.1:5000/recommend"   class="nav_item">Recommendation</a></li>
                <li><a href="http://127.0.0.1:5000/contact" class='nav_item'>Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
            <img src={{ url_for('static', filename='image/movie_wall.jpg') }} alt="movie-wall" class='grid-img'>
            <div class="container-card">
                <h2>Kevin Bacon Game</h2>
                <div class='card-item'>
                    <p>The object of the game is to start with any actor who has been in a movie and connect them to Kevin Bacon in the smallest number of links possible.</p>
                    <p>Two people are linked if they've been in a movie together.</p>
                    <p>For instance, if Mary Pickford is the targeted actor. Louise Beavers has been in the Coquette with her, then Louise Beavers is in the first degree. </p>
                    <p>It is very rarely, if the degree is higher 6.</p>
                    
                </div>
                {%if actor1%}
                <h2 class='card-item'> {{actor1}} to {{actor2}}</h2>
                <table class='card-item'>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope='col'>Result</th>
                        </tr>
                    <thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for res in result%}
                        <tr>
                            <td><i class="arrow down"></i></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class='box'>{{res}}</td>
                        </tr>
                        
                        {%endfor%}
                        
                    </tbody>
                </table>
                {%endif%}
                <h3 class='nosearch'>{{noactor1}}</h3>
                <h3 class='nosearch'>{{noactor2}}</h3>
                <button class='card-item back' type="button">
                    <a href="http://127.0.0.1:5000/game">Back to Kevin Bacon Game</a>
                </button>
                
                
              
            </div>
        </div>


    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class='contact'>
            <p>&copy; It's Movier </p>
        </div>
      <div class='icon'>
          <a href="#"><img src={{ url_for('static', filename='image/instagram.png') }} alt="instagram"></a>
          <a href="#"><img src={{ url_for('static', filename='image/facebook.png') }} alt="facebook"></a>
          <a href="#"><img src={{ url_for('static', filename='image/twitter.png') }} alt="twitter"></a>
      </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>